{"id":232864108,"title":"#問  網拍退款會這樣嗎？","content":"已經買網拍好多年了，很少遇到退款問題，幾根手指頭都數得出來那種。\n當下遇到這種問題也很錯愕，不知道這樣的問題大家有沒有遇過呢？\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/889e4cef-edd0-432e-861a-f57056f55255/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0da8c962-23e4-481e-9aaf-12a9f7e7a30e/1280.jpeg\n\n畢竟我之前遇到要退款的買家都會全額退費到銀行也沒有說到手續費的事，然後在我還沒回覆說要換成購物金的時候對方還先給我換成購物金了。\n\n後來想想實在太讓人無語，想向各位請教一下這件事。怕自己把問題放大看。","excerpt":"已經買網拍好多年了，很少遇到退款問題，幾根手指頭都數得出來那種。當下遇到這種問題也很錯愕，不知道這樣的問題大家有沒有遇過呢？畢竟我之前遇到要退款的買家都會全額退費到銀行也沒有說到手續費的事，然後在我還","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d5ee9d02-510e-4f81-96e9-ab59b56e21ca","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-10T10:08:46.411Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-10T11:41:31.952Z","commentCount":16,"likeCount":9,"tags":[],"topics":["網購","問題","心得","退貨","分享"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"網路購物","forumAlias":"buyonline","school":"購物病沒藥醫💊","department":"btssuga2","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":9}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/889e4cef-edd0-432e-861a-f57056f55255/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0da8c962-23e4-481e-9aaf-12a9f7e7a30e/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"476ce01a-39ef-4d71-8aa1-49ce2400ddf1","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/889e4cef-edd0-432e-861a-f57056f55255/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/889e4cef-edd0-432e-861a-f57056f55255/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/889e4cef-edd0-432e-861a-f57056f55255/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-10T10:08:46.411Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-10T11:41:31.952Z","width":439,"height":640},{"id":"476ce01a-39ef-4d71-8aa1-